Customers with nickel allergies have praised Clayton Jewelry Labs for carrying unique affordable fashion jewelry that anyone can wear. Our jewelry is also free from harmful metals such as lead and cadmium.   Every piece of our jewelry is packed in our branded velvet jewelry bag before shipment and inspected for manufacturer flaws, so you always receive the perfect fashion piece.
